item.title: COOKIE PARCEL BOX • 8
item.dc:creator: thenightbakeradmin
item.description: YOUR CHOICE OF 8 COOKIES. EACH COOKIE IS INDIVIDUALLY VACUUM SEALED TO RETAIN FRESHNESS DURING SHIPPING. PLEASE SELECT A DATE ON THE CHECKOUT PAGE FOR WHEN YOU WANT TO SHIP OUT YOUR COOKIES. COOKIE PARCELS ARE SHIPPED VIA CANADA POST/USPS AND DELIVERY DATES ARE SUBJECT TO THEIR SERVICES. WE CANNOT GUARANTEE A SPECIFIC DELIVERY DATE. DUE TO COVID-19, THERE MAY BE DELAYS TO CANADA/US SHIPPING. PLEASE BE PATIENT! CANADA POST IS DOING THEIR BEST TO DELIVER YOUR COOKIES SAFELY. SELECT YOUR FLAVOURS BELOW!
